title: Sarah Gigante Makes Surprise Move to AG Insurance-Soudal, Exits Movistar Contract Early
content:
The 23-year-old Australian still had one year to run on her contract with Movistar, but agrees to end it early to switch to AG Insurance-Soudal.

Read the full article at Sarah Gigante Makes Surprise Move to AG Insurance-Soudal, Exits Movistar Contract Early on Velo.
